commit.message:
Slightly improve MSVS filters generation (#2128)

* Ensure the source tree uses correct sort order, even if cached

Keep unsorted source tree in cache and sort it before returning, if
necessary, to ensure that we don't return a tree sorted in a wrong order
if it had been cached by a previous call to project.getsourcetree() with
a different "sorter" argument.

* Use the same order for standard filters as MSVS itself

Recognize the standard "Source", "Header" and "Resource Files" filters
and put them in the same order as that used by MSVS in the project files
it creates.

This avoids gratuitous differences between Premake-generated and the
existing manually created MSVS projects.

parent 16c2d6acf7f6637196d7e30182ff97b98040a57d
